    "(Note that you must commit this change afterwards for it to become effective)"
    VIEW-AS ALERT-BOX QUESTION BUTTONS YES-NO UPDATE choice AS LOGICAL.

IF choice THEN DO:
   RUN setActiveFlag(YES).
